PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1780600264
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet family of
OL,4,Cmurdered student Henry Nowak
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister has urged
OL,7,Fpoliticians to heed Mr Nowak's
OL,8,Frelatives' calls not to use the case
OL,9,F"to cause disturbances", as he accused
OL,10,FElon Musk of trying to "whip up
OL,11,Fdivision" in the UK over the murder,
OL,12,Fand after he branded Nigel Farage's
OL,13,Fresponse "unforgiveable".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@WO]rD@XOUsD@IO]uD@JOUuD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1780600264
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet family of
OL,4,Cmurdered student Henry Nowak
OL,6,FViolent protests erupted near where
OL,7,Fthe 18-year-old was fatally stabbed,
OL,8,Famid an outcry over his treatment,
OL,9,Fafter his killer Vickrum Digwa claimed
OL,10,Fhe had been the victim of a racial
OL,11,Fattack, while Mr Nowak was handcuffed
OL,12,Fby police who ignored his pleas that
OL,13,Fhe could not breathe as he lay dying.
OL,15,FBillionaire X owner Mr Musk has posted
OL,16,Fnumerous times on his platform about
OL,17,Fthe police response to the stabbing of
OL,18,Fthe teenager in Southampton last year,
OL,19,Fincluding to offer to fund a private
OL,20,Fprosecution of Hampshire Constabulary.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1780600264
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet family of
OL,4,Cmurdered student Henry Nowak
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister told reporters
OL,7,Fduring a trip to York on Thursday: "We
OL,8,Fneed to also assert who we are as a
OL,9,Fcountry, because Musk, again, has been
OL,10,Finterfering in our politics in the
OL,11,Flast few days, trying to whip up
OL,12,Fdivision ` that is not who we are in
OL,13,FBritain.
OL,15,F"In Britain, we are reasonable,
OL,16,Ftolerant people.
OL,18,F"When we have a terrible case like
OL,19,FHenry's case, Henry Nowak, we react
OL,20,Fcalmly, as his family have done."
OL,26,@oD@dOUwD@AOUzD@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1780600264
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet family of
OL,4,Cmurdered student Henry Nowak
OL,6,F"In Britain, we are reasonable,
OL,7,Ftolerant people.
OL,9,F"When we have a terrible case like
OL,10,FHenry's case, Henry Nowak, we react
OL,11,Fcalmly, as his family have done."
OL,13,FTory leader Kemi Badenoch also
OL,14,Fstressed that Mr Nowak's family "do
OL,15,Fnot want anger to tear communities
OL,16,Fapart", after meeting his mother,
OL,17,Ffather and stepmother on Thursday
OL,18,Fmorning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUsD@aO]vD@aOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1780600264
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet family of
OL,4,Cmurdered student Henry Nowak
OL,6,FShe added that the family agreed with
OL,7,Fher that "we need to bring common
OL,8,Fsense back" to how equality is treated
OL,9,Funder the law.
OL,11,FMrs Badenoch wrote on X: "They have
OL,12,Fasked that we work across political
OL,13,Fparties and religions to rebuild trust
OL,14,Fin the police.
OL,16,F"That trust has been broken because of
OL,17,Fwhat happened, and I agree with them
OL,18,Fon that.
OL,26,@oD@JOUpD@KO]sD@ZOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1780600264
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet family of
OL,4,Cmurdered student Henry Nowak
OL,6,F"We must also be prepared to examine,
OL,7,Fcarefully and seriously, religious
OL,8,Fpractices or exemptions that permit
OL,9,Fthe carrying of dangerous weapons in
OL,10,Fpublic, and other activities that are
OL,11,Fnot conducive to the public good. We
OL,12,Falso need to examine where the law
OL,13,Fneeds to change."
OL,15,FDigwa has been given a life sentence
OL,16,Fwith a minimum of 21 years in prison
OL,17,Ffor stabbing Mr Nowak with a
OL,18,Fceremonial knife with a 21cm blade,
OL,19,Fwhich he carried as part of his Sikh
OL,20,Freligion.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1780600264
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet family of
OL,4,Cmurdered student Henry Nowak
OL,6,FMr Musk has criticised on his social
OL,7,Fmedia platform "how heinously Nowak
OL,8,Fwas treated by the police in his dying
OL,9,Fmoments and how the police cravenly
OL,10,Fkowtowed to his murderer" and what he
OL,11,Fdescribed as the media's silence about
OL,12,Fthe case after writing "about George
OL,13,FFloyd millions of times".
OL,15,FIt is not the first time the tech
OL,16,Ftycoon has waded into British
OL,17,Fpolitics, having last year started a
OL,18,Fwar of words with the Government over
OL,19,Fgrooming gangs and thrown his support
OL,20,Fbehind activist Tommy Robinson.
OL,26,@oD@POUrD@YO]tD@XOUuD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1780600264
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet family of
OL,4,Cmurdered student Henry Nowak
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister, a target of Mr
OL,7,FMusk's attacks, accused the world's
OL,8,Frichest man of "spreading lies and
OL,9,Fmisinformation" at the time and has
OL,10,Falso hit out at his AI chatbot Grok
OL,11,Ffor creating sexualised images.
OL,13,FBut Mr Musk's intervention over Mr
OL,14,FNowak's murder has prompted what
OL,15,Fappears to be Sir Keir's strongest
OL,16,Fdirect condemnation of the billionaire
OL,17,Fyet.
OL,26,@pD@POUqD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1780600264
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet family of
OL,4,Cmurdered student Henry Nowak
OL,6,FSir Keir also told journalists that
OL,7,FLabour MP Jess Asato was "absolutely
OL,8,Fright" in taking legal action against
OL,9,FMr Musk's xAI over "disgusting" images
OL,10,Fcreated of her.
OL,12,FThe Conservatives, whose leader Mrs
OL,13,FBadenoch has called for an end to "two-
OL,14,Ftier policing", have said the officers
OL,15,Fwho arrested Mr Nowak on false racism
OL,16,Fclaims should face a full misconduct
OL,17,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@FO]qD@TOUqD@_O]uD@cOUvD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1780600264
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet family of
OL,4,Cmurdered student Henry Nowak
OL,6,FAsked about the Tories' demand, Sir
OL,7,FKeir said "there are questions that
OL,8,Fneed to be answered" over the police
OL,9,Fresponse, and added that the
OL,10,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,11,Fshould be given space to "get on with
OL,12,Ftheir job" in investigating the case.
OL,14,F"I think it's right that there may
OL,15,Fneed to be changes and we shouldn't
OL,16,Fshy away from that," the Labour leader
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@oD@KOUpD@TO]sD@ZOUtD@JO]vD@AOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1780600264
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet family of
OL,4,Cmurdered student Henry Nowak
OL,6,F"But we really need to listen to
OL,7,FHenry's family, because they're asking
OL,8,Fus, as politicians, as leaders, not to
OL,9,Fuse his case to whip up division, not
OL,10,Fto cause disturbances. We have to
OL,11,Flisten to them."
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Reform MP Robert Jenrick
OL,14,Fsaid it was "ludicrous" to suggest
OL,15,Fthat Mr Farage's response to the
OL,16,Fmurder was stoking division, after the
OL,17,FReform leader suggested that the
OL,18,Fpublic should feel "pure, cold rage".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@PO]vD@MOUvD@WO]zD@TOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1780600264
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet family of
OL,4,Cmurdered student Henry Nowak
OL,6,FGovernment minister Lucy Rigby earlier
OL,7,Faccused Mr Farage of effectively
OL,8,Finciting "violence against some of our
OL,9,Fbrave police officers", after nearly a
OL,10,Fdozen officers were injured in clashes
OL,11,Fwith protesters on Tuesday.
OL,13,FMr Jenrick told GB News: "I was
OL,14,Fabsolutely stunned by those ludicrous
OL,15,Fcomments.
OL,17,F"There's nothing that Nigel Farage has
OL,18,Fdone which has encouraged division.
OL,26,@pD@JOUqD@VO]uD@ZOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/14
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1780600264
OL,3,CKeir Starmer to meet family of
OL,4,Cmurdered student Henry Nowak
OL,6,F"He has simply shown leadership in
OL,7,Fsetting out the course of action that
OL,8,Fnow needs to be taken to make sure
OL,9,Fthat we fix this problem and treat
OL,10,Feverybody equally before the law."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/14
